{"tid":621134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 貿易戰掀反美潮　福州民眾街頭簽名抵制美貨","createTime":"2018-04-08T05:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T05:15:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1ba7c994295dd71372d4ee1fbf43d7b87e98adab","tid":621134,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T05:08:54.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰不斷升級，雙方不斷推出向對方加徵關稅的清單，內地民間也開始出現反美浪潮。有內地網民發現，福建福州有民眾在街頭收集簽名，呼籲民眾抵制美國貨。簽名橫額上寫着「不買美國貨、支持中國貨」，務求打贏此次中美貿易戰，引來不少人簽名響應。 <br />\n<br />\n相關照片在網上流傳，惹起熱議。不過，不少網民都認為這些活動只是「添亂」；亦有人嘲諷︰「各位，一定要小心你們的美國車了！」、「牛仔褲是美國流傳過來的，脫了吧！」、「把你們的安卓（Android）手機和蘋果手機都扔了！」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180408/mobile/bkncn-20180408112916514-0408_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180408%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20180408112916514-0408_05011_001.html&d=dkkLZikCC5jk9TNU3iTsbNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b1881f6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180408/mobile/bkncn-20180408112916514-0408_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ca11fc5d312606ead5bfdb00e00b2f614bae3111","tid":621134,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T05:09:52.000Z","msg":"把你們的安卓（Android）手機和蘋果手機都扔了！<br />\n把你們的安卓（Android）手機和蘋果手機都扔了！<br />\n<br />\n支那No IT"},{"pid":"ccd7201fe1b6c69466d75a796269c7b36cba53bd","tid":621134,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T05:12:01.000Z","msg":"應該鼓勵人用老翻才對"},{"pid":"c81de46aca615ac6414df9c8ed33aaf59dcc3780","tid":621134,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T05:12:03.000Z","msg":"好，呢單野要有咁大攪咁大"},{"pid":"d172776eb63ec09bbb85e4e7d39b7083f71b2c48","tid":621134,"uid":45213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T05:12:58.000Z","msg":"快手簽完去買iPhone"},{"pid":"3e5c2371c956b1afcd87850793480292880fb7d7","tid":621134,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T05:13:46.000Z","msg":"得啦 知啦 叻啦"},{"pid":"f77a81380ddfd4bc0cba6b2410830218a9702ba4","tid":621134,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T05:14:07.000Z","msg":"等義和團二代出黎，再八國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d94ddec480b1d2010f7bb7fd26544538820ada6","tid":621134,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4294eb2aa0a45471cae19f8e54f242b86923e168","tid":621134,"uid":93958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T05:15:56.000Z","msg":"當年咁多福州人偷渡去美國賺美國人錢唔記得晒？每個福州人總有個親戚係美日"}]}